<p>The <b>terdragon</b> can be written as a <a href="/wiki/Lindenmayer_system" class="mw-redirect" title="Lindenmayer system">Lindenmayer system</a>:
</p>
<ul><li>angle 120°</li>
<li>initial string <i>F</i></li>
<li>string rewriting rules
<ul><li><i>F</i> ↦ <i>F+F−F</i>.</li></ul></li></ul>
