<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Lévy_dragon"><span id="L.C3.A9vy_dragon"></span>Lévy dragon</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Dragon_curve&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Lévy dragon"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
